title: The 5 best-selling iPhone 6s cases on Amazon
text: If you just got a brand new iPhone 6s from Apple, you’re one of millions of happy people who can now say they’re enjoying the most powerful smartphone in the world. Apple’s new iPhone 6s features a faster processor, double the RAM, a much better camera, and sturdier construction thanks to Apple’s new 7000 Series aluminum. As sturdy as it is, however, you still want to make sure you protect your new $650+ smartphone from drops. And there’s no better way to do that than with one of the five best-selling iPhone 6s cases on Amazon.
